    <H1>Campaign Submission Process</H1>

    <DIV class="headRightCurveblk"></DIV>
    <DIV class="contentbox">

        <table width="100%" class="sectable" cellspacing="3">
            <tr>
                <td><strong>VZW Premium Messaging Guide:</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">
                    <p>
                        If you are looking for more information on premium SMS and how to launch Premium SMS or MMS
                        campaigns for
                        Verizon Wireless customers, please review the information below:
                    </p>

                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">
                    1. Content Provider reserves the shortcode via CSCA. (Please click <a
                        href="http://www.usshortcodes.com"
                        target="_blank">here</a> to access the
                    CSCA website.)
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">
                    2. VZW internal workflow tool for approving campaigns - Campaign Administrator Tool (CAT) at <A
                        href="https://psmsadmin.vzw.com/vzwcampaignadmin/index.do" class="a" target="_blank">https://psmsadmin.vzw.com</A>
                    receives daily CSC feed with VZW Assigned shortcodes.
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">
                    3. Content Provider selects one of the VZW approved content aggregators. (Please click <a
                        href="../../downloads/psms/Premium_Messaging_Referral_Sheet.pdf" target="_blank">here </a>to
                    view our
                    premium Content Aggregator referral sheet.)
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">
                    4. Shortcode is assigned to the selected aggregator within the CAT tool.
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">
                    5. Aggregator submits the campaign application in the CAT tool. (Please click <A
                        href="../../downloads/psms/VZW_Campaign_Data_Fields.xls" class="a" target="_blank">here</a> to
                    view
                    sample submission page from the tool.)
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">
                    6. Campaign goes through VZW review and approval process. (Please click <A
                        href="../../downloads/psms/CAT_tool_Approval_Process.ppt" class="a" target="_blank">here</A> for
                    an
                    overview of the VzW Premium Messaging approval process.)
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">
                    7. VZW <A href="../../downloads/psms/CAT_tool_Approval_Process.ppt" class="a" target="_blank">approval</A>
                    is sent to the aggregator within the CAT tool.
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">&nbsp;</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td width="100%">
                    <p><b>Note:</b> All content is required to be rated appropriately and <b>must</b> comply with:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Industry Best Practices (MMA guidelines) (Please click <A
                                href="../../downloads/psms/MMA_Consumer_Best_Practices.doc" class="a" target="_blank">
                            here</A>
                            to view a copy of the guidelines)
                        </li>
                        <li>VZW content guidelines (Please click <A href="http://responsibility.verizon.com/contentpolicy/" class="a" target="_blank">here</A> to view a
                            copy of
                            the VzW content guidelines)
                        </li>
                        <li>Content Aggregator agreements and SLAs</li>
                        <li>VZW review and <a href="../../downloads/psms/CAT_tool_Approval_Process.ppt" class="a"
                                              target="_blank">approval process </a></li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</div>